Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.38,0:00:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know there's an awesome\Ntreasure at the end of this sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.61,0:00:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And whoever gets it can be King\Nof the Pirates! Isn't that exciting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.18,0:00:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unheard-of adventures are waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.39,0:00:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage! Let that shred of courage grow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.26,0:00:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of\Nthe tail end to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The horizons everyone\Ndreamed of were separate at first
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.68,0:00:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now they can be seen\Nthrough a single telescope
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.82,0:00:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bitter compass of destiny\Nis leading your heart astray
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.16,0:00:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so turn the wheel in the other direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.06,0:01:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.13,0:01:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toss aside your bonds and your past
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can surely smile despite that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.38,0:01:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tears shed trying to achieve\Nyour dreams aren't for naught
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.86,0:01:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precious in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.26,0:01:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of\Nthe tail end to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.81,0:01:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to prevent Luffy and\NNami from reaching the ark,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.18,0:01:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eneru released Mamaragan. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.45,0:01:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless, Eneru.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.45,0:01:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The land won't be beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.79,0:01:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy was approaching the ark.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.46,0:02:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand over... the golden bell!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.66,0:02:03.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"God"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.46,0:02:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear with the land!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.13,0:02:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.14,0:02:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.14,0:02:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Fi... re... works!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.51,0:02:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Peony!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.51,0:02:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clear up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.19,0:02:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat! Ring the "fire of Shandora"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.86,0:02:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy finally reached the ark, and at\Nthe end of the fierce fight with Eneru...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.53,0:02:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll ring you as well!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.57,0:02:45.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"God"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.04,0:02:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.14,0:02:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Gold Rifle!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.19,0:03:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reach!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Battle Ends! Proud Fantasia Echoes Far"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.60,0:03:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear it?!\NOld diamond-head! Monkeys!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:04:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The city of gold... was right here!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.59,0:04:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bonehead did it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.76,0:04:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.26,0:04:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pretty sound! What is this?! What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.61,0:04:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believed that this moment\Nwould come one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.31,0:04:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this was the ring that Noland heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.99,0:04:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suu... I wonder if Vearth is singing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So God really... exists?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.60,0:05:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had half given up on the bell ringing\Nagain after its 400-year silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.31,0:05:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great Warrior Calgara... Can you hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.32,0:05:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the echo of the fire of Shandora...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to this land?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.67,0:05:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this tone? Could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.34,0:05:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the legendary...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hearing this... Montblanc Noland?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to have kept you waiting so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.99,0:05:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.23,0:06:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this reaches your descendants!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You like this bell's sound, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.40,0:06:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old-timer! Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.53,0:06:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.40,0:06:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one bell in\Nthis world that echoes this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.74,0:06:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is romanticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.71,0:06:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--From the sky...\N--I'm getting worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the monsters that appear\Nwith the cumuloregalis clouds,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:06:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there used to be a story like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:07:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When there is a human far up in the sky\Nand strong sunlight shines on him,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,his figure is reflected in\Nthe deep mist of the far sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shadow looks as if it's a huge monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the true form of those monsters are\Nthe shadows of the humans in the sky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then does that mean that we've already\Nconfirmed that people live in the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.78,0:07:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.78,0:07:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the story was a meaningless\Nfantasy and I'd forgotten about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.79,0:07:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it seems that it was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.13,0:07:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear the loud ring of the golden bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.47,0:07:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The city of gold really exists in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.20,0:07:46.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Noland The Liar"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.41,0:07:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noland wasn't... My ancestor wasn't a liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.11,0:07:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You rang it to tell me that from the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.32,0:08:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...right, kid? I appreciate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.66,0:08:19.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Monkey"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Old-timer?!\N--What's the matter?! Are you sick?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.81,0:08:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those kids... I'm glad they were safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.52,0:08:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was... so worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!! That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God's ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's God!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're sinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.86,0:09:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Eneru and his ship are...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...sinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.37,0:09:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bell's ring is the fire of Shandora,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a long-gone city that\Ntook pride in its prosperity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.92,0:09:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The island's singing voice that\Nproclaims the end of the battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.26,0:09:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The promised ring was\Ndelivered after 400 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.61,0:10:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although the journey of\Nthe restless island was long,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.65,0:10:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's hard to forget the distant memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.98,0:10:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, people entrusted their\Nwords in the sound of the bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They placed proud words in\Nthe song sent to the distant sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.34,0:10:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Comrades...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.68,0:10:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It rang...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.38,0:10:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder... if the old guy\Nand the others heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.15,0:10:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.00,0:11:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're... right here!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tie the ropes to strong-looking trees!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.72,0:12:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisa... Were you worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.39,0:12:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here... your treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.06,0:12:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.40,0:12:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laki...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.41,0:12:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How's everyone else?\N--They're fine! Don't speak right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.79,0:12:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.96,0:12:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! You have to get treated right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.13,0:12:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treatment can wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before treating me, do something\Nabout that guy, or he'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! His body's falling apart,\Nright down to the bones. This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.11,0:13:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's one of the guerrillas.\NWe don't owe him anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.45,0:13:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I don't really know why, but it\Nseemed like he was going all out, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.79,0:13:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What the heck?\NAre you feeling sorry for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.96,0:13:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.80,0:13:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he gonna be okay, Raccoon-Doggy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.80,0:13:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a reindeer! Look, I have antlers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.47,0:13:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. He'll survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.81,0:13:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.02,0:13:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pierre, go and rest with those Blue Sea people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.52,0:13:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pierre, hurry up and go bring the families!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.63,0:13:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, in the end, both the golden\Nbell and Eneru's golden ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.97,0:13:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think they fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.14,0:14:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So now it's a city of gold in name only, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means our journey\Nin poverty continues.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.52,0:14:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd want those dials rather than gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.19,0:14:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since we won't be able to get them\Nonce we get back to the Blue Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.69,0:14:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I wonder if Nami-san's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.02,0:14:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where Conis-chan is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.20,0:14:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay to leave Wyper\Nwith the Blue Sea people?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.54,0:14:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. It seems that\NAisa made friends with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.87,0:14:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, we have to hurry.\NIt's pointless if our enemy wakes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.21,0:14:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gather those who can move.\NWe'll banish the priests to the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.05,0:14:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.58,0:14:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you done with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,0:14:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. All he needs now is rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.59,0:14:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoo-hoo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.26,0:14:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.53,0:14:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san!! Conis-chan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.54,0:15:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! I'm glad you are okay!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.55,0:15:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so worried, but I couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conis-chan, so you were\Nworried about me that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.59,0:15:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.92,0:15:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that food, you guys? Where'd you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.92,0:15:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We found the priests' food storage\Non our way back through the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.59,0:15:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.26,0:15:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how did you get down from that height?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.60,0:15:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We used my Gum-Gum Balloon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.27,0:15:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Conis, where's your old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.27,0:15:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.94,0:15:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... um... he protected me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and then Eneru...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.59,0:16:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conis-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.44,0:16:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conis-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.60,0:16:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conis...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.27,0:16:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we're talking about you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I'm still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.11,0:16:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.15,0:16:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the White Sea on the lower level?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.82,0:16:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I found myself there\Nafter being knocked off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.32,0:16:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who came down to the lower\Nlevel heading towards Cloud End
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.99,0:16:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are also coming back to the White-White Sea\Nvia restored Milky Roads right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.83,0:16:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, since there's\Nno Angel Island anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.00,0:16:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they're heading towards Upper Yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Thank you very much.\N--Thank you very much, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:17:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no longer known by that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.99,0:17:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were all forced to work in a place\Nlike this for six long years. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We lost Angel Island, the home\Nwe were supposed to return to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.87,0:17:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Shandians, too, lost their home,\NVillage Hidden in the Clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.67,0:17:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the battle really over?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.72,0:17:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God's army is gone, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.05,0:17:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief, is the 400-year rift\Nsomething that can be filled so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.06,0:17:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Boy, I stuffed myself!\N--It's totally night now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go back to the ship now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.40,0:17:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami, what're you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.74,0:17:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! If we go back to the ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.74,0:17:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can have a long relaxed\Nsleep in a warm bed, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.68,0:17:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Usopp, you heard what she said?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.84,0:17:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's terrible. Not thinking\Nanything after seeing that,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.02,0:17:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're unqualified to be\Na pirate-- no, to be a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.38,0:18:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"That"? What're you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm returning... to where God should be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things that obstruct my field\Nof vision cannot exist in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.74,0:18:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You all were in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.45,0:18:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let anyone have it. It's fit just for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.46,0:18:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a boundless land, just like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.13,0:18:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's set off, Maxim...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.46,0:18:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To God's world that\Nfloats brightly in the night...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.87,0:18:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the land without end, the Endless Vearth!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside the ruins of Shandora.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gan Fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.12,0:19:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you shouldn't move yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... are a Skypiean!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.96,0:19:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.47,0:19:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief! Were we captured by the Skypieans?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.47,0:19:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no distinction among\Nthose injured in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.31,0:19:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The golden belfry... We still have\Nthe duty to protect it to the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.85,0:19:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.52,0:19:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the sound of drums announcing a battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.52,0:19:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's fire on the ruins, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.03,0:19:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't rush, Wyper. Wait a little\Nand see how things turn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.20,0:19:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what kind of heroic reason for\Nthe fight there was in the distant past,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.04,0:20:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to us who live in the present time,\Nthis sky is our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.54,0:20:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The land, at least, is not refusing anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.54,0:20:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But at this very moment, there's actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right... Go ahead and\Ncheck it with your own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.22,0:20:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, no one wants to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's party time!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.17,0:21:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're feeling lonely, talk to me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.68,0:21:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gaze at the heavens\Nas you wander about
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.78,0:21:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the moon,\Nyou keep your gaze constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.66,0:22:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And your deep reflection wanes\Nas you slowly disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.84,0:22:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay as you are, let those words guide you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.02,0:22:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dream, you travelers who spend\Ncountless nights drifting
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.10,0:22:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you may not be able to go back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.53,0:22:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will surely start moving forward again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.35,0:22:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold our true motive in your\Nhearts and speak not of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.52,0:23:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you learn those words?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.45,0:23:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So these are the words engraved on the belfry...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.45,0:23:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ancient weapon Poseidon?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.19,0:23:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why was Gold Roger...?\NCould the Rio Poneglyph be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.73,0:23:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're pirates, you know.\NNow, let's snatch the gold and run!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.50,0:23:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.73,0:23:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I Made It Here! The Yarn the Poneglyphs Spin"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.73,0:23:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
